name: Diversionary Tactics
Lore: 'Rebel pilots understand that what they lack in numbers, they must make up for in strategy. They often use diversions to remove dangerous opponents from a conflict.',
Text: 'If your starfighter with a pilot character aboard is in a battle, target an opponent''s starfighter present that has no characters aboard. For remainder of battle, both starfighters are power = 0, and target starfighter is forfeit = 0. (Immune to Sense.)',
